# Task #133: "Sync now" is the FAST sync — saves + light Continue only. The catalog /
# collections mirror (library-scale minutes on hardware) moved behind the honest
# "Refresh library (full, slow)" row; running it here is the regression this guards.
desc Sync now is FAST: push-pending + pull-saves + sync-continue, NEVER the catalog mirror
config paired
seeded
pick 0|Sync now
pick 2|
engine 0|RESULT ok
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --push-pending -> rc=0
expect_trace ENGINE --pull-saves -> rc=0
expect_trace ENGINE --sync-continue -> rc=0
expect_trace_absent ENGINE --mirror-catalog
expect_trace_absent ENGINE --mirror-collections
expect_trace PRES timeout=2 msg='Sync complete'
